<br>
Kill Gorilla for Library Card.  Turn in card for &quot;Book of Mischief&quot;.<br>
Kill random mobs to find the 4 &quot;corners&quot; of &quot;Words of Wealth&quot;.<br>
Place all 4 corners into the Book and combine for Words of Wealth.<br>
<br>
Give &quot;Words of Wealth&quot; to Bob the Painter for &quot;Pot of Gold&quot;.<br>
<br>
Fish up a King Cod Card, or 4 colored cards.  Turn those in to Ferjeneror to get a &quot;Deck of Spontaneous Generation&quot;.<br>
<br>
Kill mobs in zone, get cards.  Combine Cards into items. (this part should be easy to follow on POM.com)  You will need at least 2 2-Throne items (or Mask of Melodies).<br>
<br>
Combine Words and Items Created in Pot of Gold for Funny Money.<br>
<br>
Turn in 2 Funny Money to Peachy for a RANDOM box.  If you get the Wizard Box (red) congrats.<br>
<br>
Now, back to collecting cards.  Collect the cards needed for &quot;Arms of Distraction&quot;.<br>
<br>
Combine &quot;Arms of Distraction&quot; with &quot;Wily Warlock Doll&quot; (right click box to summon a doll) in the Pot of Gold to get the Wily Warlock Arms.<br>
<br>
All in all, for one item it's a pain in the ass.<br>
<br>
However, you have 5 charges per box, so once you have it you can make 5 pieces of armor.  Given you get the arms, you could have a Guildmate turn in Words of Wealth to Bob and get a pot of gold, and just combine doll and armor for him, cutting a small about of time off it.<br>
<br>
Good luck, it's a pain in the ass.<br>
<br>
-Att <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6231.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=6226.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=6218.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=6218.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6218.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=6218.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm27">PVP Forum<option value="graffeswi